::Oblitertron/DevilDuer::

DevilDuer growls as Arcangel picks up Squizzy, firing three stun shots at the 
bot. He was getting pissed. Once he got the femm away from that bot, he would 
kill it... He jumps away from some flame, returning fire at Decadel
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
The ground shakes slightly as a shadow covers all the bots there, Oblitertron 
walking up, standing to block Arcangel's path. With a command from DevilDuer, 
Oblitertron turns his head, firing his optics at Arcangel and sweeping down a 
huge hand to grab Squizzy.

"She's Alliance property," DevilDuer growls at Arcangel as he watches 
Oblitertron attack, "And messing with the Alliance is a bad idea."
